1
00:00:06,840 --> 00:00:09,820
You never eat on time—

2
00:00:09,920 --> 00:00:11,400
especially breakfast—

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:13,140
and it makes me

4
00:00:13,140 --> 00:00:14,620
suffer terribly.

5
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:17,140
I endure it all day, and when it finally

6
00:00:17,140 --> 00:00:19,200
gets late at night, you start eating.

7
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:22,600
After you eat, you fall asleep,

8
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,440
while I...

9
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:27,240
have to spend the entire night, again and again,

10
00:00:27,240 --> 00:00:29,620
working hard to digest all that food.

11
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:35,600
You're so cruel to me.

12
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:42,840
Drink the medicine quickly.

13
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:43,920
The medicine can suppress her.

14
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:45,360
Stop struggling.

15
00:00:45,540 --> 00:00:46,620
Let's go to

16
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:48,680
the underworld together.

17
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:57,030
Drink the medicine now!

18
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:59,820
This is between us.

19
00:00:59,820 --> 00:01:02,120
It's none of your business...

20
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:50,880
Am I... really going to die?

21
00:02:53,060 --> 00:02:54,120
From today onward,

22
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:56,100
take your medicine on time every day.

23
00:02:56,100 --> 00:02:57,300
You need to eat the meals

24
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:59,300
I prepare for you, three times a day.

25
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:02,420
You must go to bed before 9 PM every night.

26
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,280
You must not overindulge in food,

27
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,040
get angry,

28
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:05,800
be sad,

29
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,680
worry,

30
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,800
stay up all night,

31
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,680
exhaust yourself,

32
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,720
or do anything harmful to your body.

33
00:03:10,940 --> 00:03:11,660
Okay!

34
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,200
No need to wait until 9 PM.

35
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,480
I'll sleep right now.

36
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,880
Do you think I want to live like this?

37
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:34,900
We work until late every day.

38
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,800
Even after we're off duty,

39
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:39,880
Lady Zhao still makes us keep working.

40
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:44,260
When we're done, we sleep.

41
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:46,940
When we wake up, we work again.

42
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,260
As for food,

43
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:51,980
it's just leftovers from the Imperial Kitchen.

44
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,640
Even so,

45
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:02,040
I still want to do something I truly want to do.

46
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:06,080
Even if it's just for an hour.

47
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:08,560
To read

48
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,640
some novels.

49
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:12,880
At least this way,

50
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,480
I can fool myself into thinking

51
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,920
that my life is my own,

52
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,480
not owned by work.

53
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,360
Perhaps...

54
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:34,460
this is just the fate of us commoners.

55
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,120
How long...

56
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,180
does it take you...

57
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:45,240
to forget someone who's passed away?

58
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:50,480
You've been married into our family for a year now!

59
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:52,300
Why haven't you

60
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:53,740
gotten pregnant yet?

61
00:04:54,540 --> 00:04:57,670
Even a hen would've laid several clutches of eggs by now!

62
00:04:57,820 --> 00:04:59,460
Are you plotting something in your heart?

63
00:04:59,460 --> 00:05:00,100
No.

64
00:05:04,420 --> 00:05:05,420
Drink this bowl of

65
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:06,580
cow dung soup!

66
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:09,880
I had an old imperial physician prepare it specially!

67
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,240
Drink it!

68
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,640
Drink!

69
00:05:25,540 --> 00:05:27,940
