117
00:08:13,780 --> 00:08:15,660
I really envy them.

118
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,800
If Chang'e and the Jade Rabbit can go,

119
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:25,760
then you and I can go too, right?

120
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,880
I really want to go there.

121
00:08:33,059 --> 00:08:34,700
That place...

122
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:40,559
must be a place of true happiness.

123
00:09:06,860 --> 00:09:08,340
Little White Fox...

124
00:09:09,180 --> 00:09:10,660
I'm so cold...

125
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,280
I'm so cold...

126
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:22,270
Little White Fox...

127
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:32,580
First bow to heaven and earth!

128
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:35,840
Second bow to the parents!

129
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:39,540
Husband and wife bow to each other!

130
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:41,960
Ceremony complete!

131
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:44,940
Escort the couple to the bridal chamber!

132
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:49,500
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

133
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:58,940
Little...

134
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:01,780
White Fox...

135
00:10:22,340 --> 00:10:24,320
Don't worry about me.

136
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:27,140
I heard his son is very kind.

137
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:29,060
Take good care of yourself.

138
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:30,540
I will also...

139
00:10:30,540 --> 00:10:32,100
live a very happy life.

140
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,160
Am I really...

141
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:46,700
going to die?

142
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:47,900
You'll be fine.

143
00:10:57,260 --> 00:10:58,460
I really hope

144
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:00,300
I can see my dad

145
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:01,760
one more time before I die.

146
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:04,460
You'll be fine.

147
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,060
Oh, right,

148
00:11:08,060 --> 00:11:08,960
about the Imperial Servants Bureau...

149
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,760
I said,

150
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,040
you'll be fine.

151
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,800
What's wrong?

152
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,410
Why are you so agitated?

153
00:11:15,860 --> 00:11:17,440
Do you remember what I told you?

154
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:19,180
Holding hands can do many things

155
00:11:19,180 --> 00:11:20,620
and cure all ailments.

156
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,240
During this time,

157
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,880
just rest well.

158
00:11:25,020 --> 00:11:26,960
If our palace maids'

159
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,020
withheld wages...

160
00:11:28,700 --> 00:11:29,500
Alright.

161
00:11:30,060 --> 00:11:31,300
Rest easy.

162
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:32,760
Leave these matters to me.

163
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:37,020
Didn't you say you didn't want to meddle in such things?

164
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:39,730
Anything related to you

165
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,540
is never trivial to me.

166
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,280
May I ask

167
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:54,420
why Your Grace summoned

168
00:11:54,420 --> 00:11:55,740
this servant today?

169
00:11:55,740 --> 00:11:56,740
Two things.

170
00:11:57,460 --> 00:11:58,260
First,

171
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,760
return every copper of the wages

172
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,890
you previously withheld to everyone.

173
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:04,360
Second,

174
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:05,720
after work hours,

175
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:08,320
you are forbidden to make them work anymore.

176
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,400
Your Grace,

177
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:12,140
the palace has its own rules.

178
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:13,020
Rewards and punishments

179
00:12:13,020 --> 00:12:14,220
are clearly defined.

180
00:12:14,580 --> 00:12:15,580
If I really carry out your orders,

181
00:12:15,580 --> 00:12:18,220
how is this servant supposed to manage the bureau?

182
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:20,260
Lady Zhao, are you genuinely managing the bureau,

183
00:12:20,260 --> 00:12:21,800
or are you using it as a pretext

184
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:23,560
to oppress others?

185
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:25,800
I presume Your Grace

186
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:28,600
must have been incited by that girl, Huo Xiangjiu.

187
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,600
It's not that this servant dares to disobey,

188
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,480
but

189
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,680
I'm worried

190
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:33,620
that Your Grace cannot

191
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:35,080
bear the consequences of this matter.

192
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,080
You cannot.

193
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,720
Lady Zhao,

194
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,840
are you threatening me?

195
00:12:51,420 --> 00:12:52,460
My heavens.

196
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:58,540
I wouldn't dare.

197
00:12:58,540 --> 00:12:59,620
This servant wouldn't dare.

198
00:12:59,620 --> 00:13:01,380
Even with ten times the courage,

199
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:03,510
I'd never dare to threaten Your Grace.

200
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:06,540
It's just that this matter

201
00:13:06,540 --> 00:13:07,800
is extremely serious.

202
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,360
It concerns more than just

203
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,960
a small Imperial Servants Bureau.

204
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,760
I beg Your Grace to reconsider carefully.

205
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:14,490
Please reconsider carefully.

206
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,800
Are you telling me what to do?

207
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:19,740
No, no, no.

208
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:21,780
Since Your Grace has spoken,

209
00:13:21,780 --> 00:13:23,740
this servant will carry out your orders.

210
00:13:23,740 --> 00:13:27,100
I'll act according to Your Grace's orders.

211
00:13:36,700 --> 00:13:38,640
Lord Feng is no different from the rest.

212
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,840
These damn men

213
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,840
lose all sense when they see a woman.

214
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:44,760
I think Huo Xiangjiu will be the death of Lord Feng!

215
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:47,920
Let's see how I deal with this pair

216
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:49,240
of scoundrels!

217
00:13:51,100 --> 00:13:53,660
Just you wait.

218
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:00,080
Put me down!

219
00:14:01,140 --> 00:14:02,200
What are you doing?

220
00:14:03,140 --> 00:14:04,660
Put me down!

221
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:19,660
Your Highness,

222
00:14:20,020 --> 00:14:21,280
what is all this about?

223
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:26,220
I'm bored.

224
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:26,860
So I had you brought here

225
00:14:26,860 --> 00:14:27,790
to entertain me.

226
00:14:28,180 --> 00:14:29,780
Using me for entertainment?

227
00:14:29,860 --> 00:14:32,700
You were never properly castrated, yet you still infiltrated the palace.

228
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,760
And you even dared to take liberties with me.

229
00:14:34,760 --> 00:14:36,360
Using you for entertainment

230
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:37,860
is perfectly justified.

231
00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:42,200
Your Highness,

232
00:14:42,660 --> 00:14:44,540
I did help you reconcile with the Old Madam,

233
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:45,540
didn't I?

234
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:47,940
That's precisely why

235
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:49,700
you're still alive.

236
00:14:50,660 --> 00:14:51,500
Otherwise,

237
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,920
I'd have killed you already.

238
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:58,080
Wait, wait!

239
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,440
Your Highness! Your Highness!

240
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,000
If you want entertainment,

241
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,360
let me tell you a joke.

242
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,560
Jokes are fun!

243
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:04,400
Laugh once,

244
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:05,320
and you'll feel ten years younger.

245
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:06,160
Laugh twice,

246
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:08,090
and you'll feel like a child again.

247
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:11,240
Fine.

248
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:15,440
But if your joke isn't funny,

249
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:17,860
I'll have to entertain myself my way.

250
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:28,800
Got one.

251
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:30,840
Tell me,

252
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,000
is the Grim Reaper

253
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,800
divine or demonic?

254
00:15:35,540 --> 00:15:36,740
How would I know that?

255
00:15:36,780 --> 00:15:37,620
Obviously,

256
00:15:37,620 --> 00:15:38,900
he must be divine.

257
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:39,560
Otherwise,

258
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:40,620
we'd just call him

259
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:41,910
"you old devil."

260
00:15:46,540 --> 00:15:47,300
Old devil...

261
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:58,160
Have you started telling your joke?

262
00:15:58,580 --> 00:15:59,510
I just finished.

263
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,660
Are you messing with me?

264
00:16:02,660 --> 00:16:04,260
What I just said was the joke.

265
00:16:06,900 --> 00:16:08,180
Wait, wait!

266
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:09,780
Let me think of another one for Your Highness!

267
00:16:09,780 --> 00:16:10,840
Let me think again!

268
00:16:10,900 --> 00:16:11,830
Another joke...

269
00:16:14,140 --> 00:16:15,140
Got it.

270
00:16:16,420 --> 00:16:18,380
Cats go "meow meow meow."

271
00:16:18,540 --> 00:16:20,080
Dogs go "hah hah hah."

272
00:16:20,420 --> 00:16:22,260
Ducks go "quack quack quack."

273
00:16:22,420 --> 00:16:23,350
What do bees say?

274
00:16:26,260 --> 00:16:27,580
Bees say...

275
00:16:27,580 --> 00:16:29,060
"Bee prepared."

276
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:44,300
This one...

277
00:16:44,620 --> 00:16:46,420
This one isn't funny either, eh?

278
00:16:47,180 --> 00:16:49,820
When exactly are you going to start your joke?

279
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:52,480
Your Highness!

280
00:16:54,740 --> 00:16:55,540
What's wrong?

281
00:16:56,300 --> 00:16:57,140
The directors of the Palace Service Bureau and Imperial Wardrobe Bureau—

282
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:57,700
the heads

283
00:16:57,800 --> 00:16:59,860
of the six bureaus and twenty-four departments—

284
00:16:59,860 --> 00:17:02,300
all of them have gone to Fucang Palace to make trouble for Huo Xiangjiu!

285
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:03,340
What's the trouble about?

286
00:17:03,340 --> 00:17:04,140
They say

287
00:17:04,260 --> 00:17:07,579
Lord Feng is interfering with the management of their offices!

288
00:17:07,579 --> 00:17:09,700
We demand to see His Grace!

289
00:17:09,700 --> 00:17:11,180
We must see His Grace immediately!

290
00:17:11,180 --> 00:17:15,140
We insist on seeing His Grace!

291
00:17:15,140 --> 00:17:16,740
I've been managing the bureau for 30 years.

292
00:17:16,740 --> 00:17:18,780
This implies we're incompetent!

